name: Perrissa Varner
text: I went to Spa Therapy and Ms Amy assisted me! She was very professional and sweet! I went in feeling stiff due to a recent surgery and when I left I could already feel a MAJOR difference! Ms Amy was very attentive to all of my needs and accommodated me in every way! The massage area was very clean and relaxing! She was not in any rush and made me feel like I had been a customer for years! I will not go anywhere else this is my new Massage Spot! Lol!

name: Shona Malhotra
text: Vivian is amazing!!! My skin is doing so much better after going consistently and all of her recommendations for products I can start using from Target were wonderful!

name: Kristin Wright
text: Best massage. Will be back! Very friendly, clean place to go!

name: Theresa Byrne
text: Nice lady Ms Amy is awesome

name: patti hall
text: If you need a deep tissue massage, Amy does a great job.   Both times I have gone she has known exactly where to concentrate the most time to help me leave feeling much better than when I arrived.  Professional,  on time and you get a full hour!   I will be back

name: Candace Jaggars
text:
Such a beautiful place inside; so neat and homey, and the owner is so sweet.
Massage therapist Kirk is amazing! He listens when I tell him my issues and relieves so much of my pain almost instantly. I can't wait to continue our work to a pain free body. I highly recommend!

name: Lizzy Kate Skinner
text: Spa therapy is absolutely AMAZING!! I would 100% recommend! Kirk is amazing and his massages are out of this world! I feel so much better and more relaxed every time I get a massage from him!

text: I got my first Brazilian wax today and I couldn’t be happier!  DeAnna was extremely fast and friendly! The atmosphere was calm and refreshing. I already booked my next session!!!

text: Great place and very relaxing! Sandy and her crew are always nice and very personable.
